{"tid":1643259,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲有咁多人幫親東海堂（美心旗下）！","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:34:59.000Z","uid":277912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec8377fb574fc7f2f11d464dfc643027a4e2759","tid":1643259,"uid":277912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.maxims.com.hk/tc/about/cat_01_a.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.maxims.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Fcat_01_a.asp&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em%2BEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=6abaf2ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.maxims.com.hk/tc/about/cat_01_a.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n美心西餅由1960年代的咖啡廳餅店，發展至香港最具規模之西餅連鎖店，擁有180多間分店，遍布港、九、新界港鐵沿線。美心西餅帶領面包及蛋糕新熱潮，由材料、款式以至店鋪裝修均充滿無限創意，為顧客不斷推出各款新鮮美味的產品。於2005年起，在廣州開設廠房及旗艦店，以配合華南地區迅速發展的需求，現時分店已逾100間。2008年，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美心集團正式收購香港「東海堂有限公司」，經營全港逾70間「東海堂」，</span></strong>集團亦繼續進一步拓展高級日本西餅及面包市場，並於2010年推出全新概念店arome BAKERY ROOM。於2012年創立的URBAN，除了創下開業一年間售出超過一百萬個牛角酥的紀錄，更不斷優化品牌，創立藝術概念輕食餐廳URBAN Bakery Works，印證「烘焙也是一種藝術」的型格餐飲體驗。2015年Maxim&rsquo;s Cake Lab成立，糅合美心西餅優良傳統及現今流行的精品西餅店概念，體現不斷創新、追求更精致美食的信念。近期力作還有Paper Stone Bakery，以傳統手工加上嚴選優質食材，炮制出融彙亞洲風味的歐陸面包。"},{"pid":"a1f5b1ed635bc8f3304e567440ba6aabdd5294dd","tid":1643259,"uid":66822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:04:21.000Z","msg":"星期五中環快閃 撐被捕保安<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FoM1jNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFoM1jNJ.jpg&h=eaa6b73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7onWS7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7onWS7K.jpg&h=4e446c9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f72175e746c6e7fd6c92f1c03339bfe0c9c2b359","tid":1643259,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:04:39.000Z","msg":"罷買"},{"pid":"89ca34ea2ff3d70bf6806aacd1e0c4b63d7eee15","tid":1643259,"uid":308419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:34:59.000Z","msg":"[美心罷食]機場員工/東涌居民留意!!! 伍淑清係世界之窗老闆<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ekMsuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ekMsuS</a>"}]}